sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy)
    participant Authorino as Authorino
    participant Limitador as Limitador
    participant MaaS as MaaS Controller
    participant AIGW as AI Gateway<br/>Payload Processing
    participant NeMo as NeMo Guardrails
    participant ExtLLM as External LLM Provider

    Note over Client,ExtLLM: Workflow 5: Guardrailed LLM Inference (MaaS + Guardrails)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(HTTPS/443, API key header)

    Gateway->>Authorino: AuthPolicy evaluation
    Authorino->>MaaS: Validate API key<br/>(MaaS API callback)
    Authorino->>Authorino: Check group membership
    Authorino->>Limitador: Evaluate rate limits
    Limitador-->>Authorino: Rate limit OK
    Authorino-->>Gateway: Authenticated + authorized

    Gateway->>AIGW: ext_proc invocation<br/>(request phase)
    AIGW->>AIGW: Resolve model<br/>(ExternalModel CR lookup)
    AIGW->>AIGW: Translate API format<br/>(normalize to provider format)

    AIGW->>NeMo: Evaluate INPUT rails
    NeMo->>NeMo: Jailbreak detection
    NeMo->>NeMo: PII filtering
    NeMo->>NeMo: Content safety check
    NeMo-->>AIGW: Input rails: PASS

    AIGW->>AIGW: Inject provider credentials
    AIGW->>ExtLLM: Forward to provider<br/>(HTTPS/443, provider API key)
    ExtLLM-->>AIGW: Completion response

    AIGW->>NeMo: Evaluate OUTPUT rails
    NeMo->>NeMo: Response content safety
    NeMo->>NeMo: Factuality check
    NeMo-->>AIGW: Output rails: PASS

    AIGW->>AIGW: Translate response<br/>(provider to OpenAI format)
    AIGW-->>Gateway: Filtered response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(HTTPS/443)
